WEBVTT

WEBVTT

00:01:58.226 --> 00:01:59.640
Bedtime!

00:02:00.520 --> 00:02:02.213
Whoo-hoo! Bedtime!

00:02:02.213 --> 00:02:03.238
Yeah!

00:02:03.238 --> 00:02:04.238
oh nooo

00:02:07.580 --> 00:02:09.686
Did you wash your face?

00:02:09.686 --> 00:02:10.780
Yes.

00:02:11.432 --> 00:02:12.504
No.

00:02:15.997 --> 00:02:17.704
Story time! Story time!

00:02:17.704 --> 00:02:19.411
-Whee!
-Yes!

00:02:22.735 --> 00:02:23.735
Shh.

00:02:28.304 --> 00:02:32.637
Once upon a time.
there was a brave and noble princess

00:02:32.637 --> 00:02:34.504
named Peach.

00:02:34.504 --> 00:02:38.146
'She was the great protector
of the Mushroom Kingdom.'

00:02:38.146 --> 00:02:40.677
‘Her story began many years ago.’

00:02:40.677 --> 00:02:44.030
I want to hear the story
about the plumbers.

00:02:44.030 --> 00:02:46.366
We did that one last night

00:02:46.366 --> 00:02:48.980
and the night before.
and the night before.

00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:51.839
-Plumber. Plumber.
-Plumber.

00:02:51.839 --> 00:02:54.706
-Plumber! Plumber!
-Plumber! Plumber!

00:02:54.706 --> 00:02:56.306
-Okay.
-Whoo-hoo!

00:02:56.306 --> 00:02:58.298
I'm hooked on the brothers

00:02:59.885 --> 00:03:01.374
Mario and Luigi…

00:03:01.374 --> 00:03:04.428
Get to the Donkey Kong part!

00:03:04.428 --> 00:03:08.059
-Donkey Kong! Donkey Kong!
-Donkey Kong! Donkey Kong!

00:03:08.059 --> 00:03:11.215
Donkey Kong! Donkey--

00:03:16.952 --> 00:03:20.539
Let's save the rest for tomorrow.

00:03:20.539 --> 00:03:23.344
- You all get tucked into bed. Alright?
- Boo

00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:28.207
I'll be right back.

00:03:46.237 --> 00:03:50.604
Princess Rosalina.
you're coming with me.

00:04:43.270 --> 00:04:46.581
-You messed with the wrong--
-Mama.

00:04:47.336 --> 00:04:49.047
I had a bad dream.

00:04:50.409 --> 00:04:52.779
Uh-oh. It wasn't a dream.

00:05:34.189 --> 00:05:37.011
From the ashes of his father's defeat

00:05:37.011 --> 00:05:38.922
rises a new conqueror.

00:05:38.922 --> 00:05:43.211
The 'Bowser' name
shall be feared once more!

00:05:44.931 --> 00:05:48.789
-Will you shut up?
-I'm just so happy for you.

00:05:48.789 --> 00:05:51.679
Your first princess nabbing!

00:05:53.011 --> 00:05:54.811
Leave my mom alone!

00:05:56.365 --> 00:05:57.125
No!

00:06:49.913 --> 00:06:51.024
Wahoo!

00:07:14.838 --> 00:07:15.752
Whoo-hoo!

00:07:45.522 --> 00:07:48.233
Lu! That jump you hit back there!

00:07:48.233 --> 00:07:52.277
-Mario. are we cool motorcycle guys now?
-Obviously.

00:07:52.277 --> 00:07:54.211
Oh! You're here!

00:07:54.211 --> 00:07:57.277
Now. where's the troubled pipe?

00:08:00.324 --> 00:08:03.419
Okay. okay. How about pointing?

00:09:13.547 --> 00:09:16.961
Okay. I guess we'll just
follow that terrifying noise.

00:09:25.128 --> 00:09:27.772
Come on. You're not
the scared guy anymore.

00:09:28.860 --> 00:09:31.544
Yes I am! People don't change

00:09:49.411 --> 00:09:51.134
There's the problem.

00:10:05.382 --> 00:10:07.288
Put the bricks back!
Put the bricks back!

00:10:07.288 --> 00:10:09.050
I looked back down that hole

00:10:09.050 --> 00:10:11.213
and then double looked back

00:10:27.814 --> 00:10:30.664
Hey. It's all right.

00:10:39.655 --> 00:10:41.498
Easy.

00:10:49.803 --> 00:10:51.937
Okay. Okay now.

00:10:51.937 --> 00:10:53.685
What's your name. little guy?

00:10:53.685 --> 00:10:54.968
Yoshi.

00:10:54.968 --> 00:10:56.618
Nice to meet you. Yoshi.

00:10:56.618 --> 00:10:59.001
How did you get in a warp pipe?

00:11:23.516 --> 00:11:25.118
"Out of the road!’

00:11:51.887 --> 00:11:53.646
Oh.

00:12:04.664 --> 00:12:06.346
I guess we'll never know.

00:12:12.737 --> 00:12:14.219
Found the problem.

00:12:21.713 --> 00:12:23.739
-Hola. Yoshi!
-Yoshi?

00:12:23.739 --> 00:12:26.958
Yoshi. Yoshi. Yoshi

00:12:28.291 --> 00:12:30.897
All that trouble over a Yoshi.

00:12:30.897 --> 00:12:33.501
Yeah. You know.
we found the little fella and…

00:12:35.430 --> 00:12:36.830
Where'd he go?

00:12:38.519 --> 00:12:41.809
Hmm. He seemed like a nice guy

00:12:45.495 --> 00:12:46.784
Vroom. vroom.

00:12:48.386 --> 00:12:50.789
He knows that's my bike. right?

00:12:55.197 --> 00:12:58.421
Aaah!

00:13:32.121 --> 00:13:34.550
Where are you taking us?

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:36.831
Try and enjoy it. Princess.

00:13:36.831 --> 00:13:40.276
It's the last place
you'll ever see alive.

00:14:36.656 --> 00:14:38.602
It's pretty cool. right?

00:14:38.602 --> 00:14:41.603
I really think my dad's gonna love it.

00:14:44.910 --> 00:14:46.875
Mama. I'm scared.

00:14:46.875 --> 00:14:48.812
It's gonna be alright.

00:15:02.553 --> 00:15:07.053
My Koopas!
Guess who stole a princess!

00:15:07.053 --> 00:15:08.329
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:15:08.329 --> 00:15:10.450
And not just any princess.

00:15:10.450 --> 00:15:14.434
The guardian of the cosmos.
the mother of the stars.

00:15:14.434 --> 00:15:18.407
With her powers.
we will destroy the universe!

00:15:18.407 --> 00:15:21.928
She will give her life
for our glory!

00:15:21.928 --> 00:15:22.841
[all] Yeah!

00:15:22.841 --> 00:15:24.932
How's that for a speech

00:15:24.932 --> 00:15:26.827
Very descriptive

00:15:30.303 --> 00:15:31.505
Ow!

00:15:32.932 --> 00:15:37.218
No one hurts my kid!

00:15:41.798 --> 00:15:42.759
Go!

00:16:03.202 --> 00:16:06.681
The great battle of my life draws near

00:16:06.681 --> 00:16:09.992
It is time to free my father!

00:16:34.162 --> 00:16:35.518
Think she'll like it?

00:16:35.518 --> 00:16:39.233
Mario. do you have
feelings for the Princess?

00:16:39.233 --> 00:16:40.146
What?!

00:16:42.134 --> 00:16:45.401
Can't a guy give his good buddy
a perfect present

00:16:45.401 --> 00:16:47.386
to show her just how much
she means to him?

00:16:47.725 --> 00:16:51.728
"When the moon hits your eye"

00:16:51.728 --> 00:16:54.486
"Like a big pizza pie. that's--"

00:16:54.486 --> 00:16:56.844
"a-<i>yoshi</i> "

00:16:57.121 --> 00:16:59.077
I'm not in love with Peach!

00:17:01.538 --> 00:17:02.783
Let's just go.

00:17:25.355 --> 00:17:26.917
-Hey. guys!
-Hey!

00:17:26.917 --> 00:17:28.977
Toad! looking good.

00:17:30.417 --> 00:17:32.617
Um. who is this?

00:17:34.110 --> 00:17:34.977
Yoshi.

00:17:35.647 --> 00:17:38.390
Who can resist that face

00:17:40.162 --> 00:17:41.123
Come on!

00:17:42.308 --> 00:17:45.860
So. some cool dinosaur just shows up.
and he's now part of the group.

00:17:53.329 --> 00:17:56.010
-Hey uh. have you seen the Princess?
-No.

00:18:29.167 --> 00:18:30.967
Hey.

00:18:30.967 --> 00:18:32.634
You're missing your own party.

00:18:33.800 --> 00:18:36.400
I hate birthdays.

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:37.604
Yeah…

00:18:37.604 --> 00:18:40.134
Luigi spent his 10th birthday crying.

00:18:40.134 --> 00:18:43.645
said his childhood was over.

00:18:44.537 --> 00:18:48.813
Well. the crazy thing is.
today is not my real birthday.

00:18:49.035 --> 00:18:51.369
It's just the day the Toads found me.

00:18:51.681 --> 00:18:54.165
They have no idea where I came from.

00:18:54.791 --> 00:18:57.696
I've lived my entire life wondering

00:18:57.696 --> 00:18:59.475
where my family is.

00:18:59.931 --> 00:19:02.010
That must be so hard.

00:19:02.010 --> 00:19:05.274
Sometimes I just feel so lost

00:19:08.720 --> 00:19:10.843
Guess that it's not
your actual birthday.

00:19:11.484 --> 00:19:12.966
You don't want a present?

00:19:12.966 --> 00:19:14.288
Mario!

00:19:14.288 --> 00:19:16.651
Alright! Fine. fine.

00:19:21.012 --> 00:19:21.979
Oh.

00:19:26.569 --> 00:19:27.703
I love it.

00:19:38.245 --> 00:19:39.369
Whoa.

00:19:53.591 --> 00:19:54.635
Look.

00:21:26.824 --> 00:21:30.702
Princess Peach.
I've finally found you.

00:21:30.702 --> 00:21:31.979
Oh!

00:21:40.359 --> 00:21:41.735
Feel better now?

00:21:44.338 --> 00:21:46.784
I can't believe it's really you.

00:21:46.784 --> 00:21:50.246
Our Mama read so many
bedtime stories about you.

00:21:50.876 --> 00:21:51.715
Me?

00:21:52.259 --> 00:21:53.482
Are you sure?

00:21:53.482 --> 00:21:56.030
She says anything
ever happens to her.

00:21:56.030 --> 00:21:58.330
to find you and you'd help us.

00:21:59.213 --> 00:22:02.446
Princess. our Mama's been taken.

00:22:02.446 --> 00:22:03.543
What happened?

00:22:03.543 --> 00:22:06.314
A giant robot took her
to a scary planet

00:22:06.314 --> 00:22:08.625
out beyond the Gateway Galaxy.

00:22:08.625 --> 00:22:09.990
Can you help us?

00:22:14.670 --> 00:22:16.582
Peach. sorry. I--

00:22:16.582 --> 00:22:18.887
Yes. yes. We
were eavesdropping.

00:22:18.887 --> 00:22:21.111
-Don't even think about leaving...
-Guys.

00:22:21.111 --> 00:22:23.278
Can we just give the Princess a minute?

00:22:23.278 --> 00:22:24.855
She'll figure out what to do.

00:22:24.855 --> 00:22:27.184
I disagree. Mario.

00:22:27.184 --> 00:22:29.153
Even though my pajamas
say otherwise.

00:22:29.153 --> 00:22:32.905
There is nothing to figure out.
She is not leaving!

00:22:32.905 --> 00:22:34.494
-Yes.
-Alright. guys.

00:22:34.494 --> 00:22:37.364
Let's go. We'll discuss
more in the morning.

00:22:39.538 --> 00:22:41.277
Good night. Princess.

00:22:51.125 --> 00:22:53.494
Toad. pack our things.

00:23:31.753 --> 00:23:34.282
Whoo-hoo-hoo!

00:23:41.157 --> 00:23:42.243
What happened?

00:23:42.243 --> 00:23:44.331
She left this for you.

00:23:47.179 --> 00:23:50.156
'Dear Mustache.
I've gone to the Gateway Galaxy'

00:23:50.156 --> 00:23:52.398
‘to begin my search
for the Luma's mom.'

00:23:52.398 --> 00:23:54.506
'I'm leaving the kingdom
in your hands.’

00:23:54.968 --> 00:23:57.432
'Sincerely. Peach.'

00:23:59.266 --> 00:24:02.792
"Sincerely"? Ooh-la-la.
that's a good sign.

00:24:02.792 --> 00:24:04.848
Princess Peach is gone?

00:24:04.848 --> 00:24:06.536
Oh. no!

00:24:10.403 --> 00:24:12.689
Everyone. calm down.

00:24:13.878 --> 00:24:17.271
The Super Mario Brothers
can take care of the kingdom.

00:25:25.303 --> 00:25:26.467
Whoo-hoo!

00:26:01.556 --> 00:26:03.168
Now what?

00:26:37.734 --> 00:26:39.219
Hey. big guy!

00:26:40.986 --> 00:26:42.359
You scared me!

00:26:42.359 --> 00:26:43.770
You wanted to see us?

00:26:43.770 --> 00:26:46.085
Don't move. I'll be right out.

00:26:48.566 --> 00:26:50.782
"Sip in the soup…"

00:26:50.782 --> 00:26:52.330
"Clean up the paint"

00:26:55.466 --> 00:26:58.178
"And also trim
the bonsai bush"

00:26:58.178 --> 00:26:59.144
Here we go!

00:27:04.656 --> 00:27:06.744
Ha-ha! Hey. Luigi!

00:27:08.287 --> 00:27:10.134
What's up. Mario?

00:27:11.423 --> 00:27:15.535
Behold! I made a masterpiece
for Princess Peach.

00:27:16.316 --> 00:27:17.316
What do you think?

00:27:17.883 --> 00:27:19.609
And be honest.

00:27:20.949 --> 00:27:22.755
Love the colors.

00:27:23.713 --> 00:27:27.228
The criticism I give you is
"It's trash."

00:27:27.579 --> 00:27:30.205
How dare you look at
my masterpiece and say that?

00:27:30.205 --> 00:27:32.047
You think painting is easy?

00:27:32.047 --> 00:27:35.583
I'll burn the skin of your bones!

00:27:36.228 --> 00:27:37.741
Wow!

00:27:38.198 --> 00:27:39.324
I'm sorry about that.

00:27:39.324 --> 00:27:41.054
That's the old Bowser talking.

00:27:41.054 --> 00:27:45.369
Ha! Still working through
my demons. I suppose.

00:27:46.065 --> 00:27:48.525
All good. All better now.

00:27:48.525 --> 00:27:51.674
Anyway. it's not just a present.

00:27:51.674 --> 00:27:53.371
It's a peace offering.

00:27:53.371 --> 00:27:54.870
I'd like her to release me.

00:27:54.870 --> 00:27:56.034
Not for good behavior.

00:27:56.034 --> 00:27:58.421
For awesome behavior.

00:27:58.421 --> 00:28:00.177
She'll never release you.

00:28:00.177 --> 00:28:02.487
And don't even ask about
making you big again.

00:28:02.487 --> 00:28:04.919
Even though I'm totally rehabilitated?

00:28:04.919 --> 00:28:06.798
Mario. he's really changed.

00:28:06.798 --> 00:28:09.218
We're doing a weekly book club together.

00:28:09.218 --> 00:28:10.643
I bring the soup!

00:28:10.643 --> 00:28:14.323
She doesn't trust you.
and neither do I.

00:28:14.934 --> 00:28:19.596
Oh. you better start trusting me.
or I will eat your soul! and--

00:28:22.225 --> 00:28:25.036
I'm sorry. It's just… Oh. wow.

00:28:25.455 --> 00:28:27.377
Alright. You know what guys?

00:28:27.377 --> 00:28:28.867
I'm gonna hit the sack.

00:28:28.867 --> 00:28:32.565
I need my 8 hours.
or else I really turn into a monster.

00:28:33.090 --> 00:28:34.695
Aah! Ow!

00:28:43.852 --> 00:28:45.474
Hehe. Nighty night

00:29:41.776 --> 00:29:43.818
We gotta get everyone out of here.

00:29:43.818 --> 00:29:45.551
Go! go! go!

00:30:27.698 --> 00:30:29.505
That's everyone. Let's go.

00:30:51.171 --> 00:30:52.736
Mamma mia

00:30:55.438 --> 00:30:56.562
Wow.

00:31:19.719 --> 00:31:21.819
In the name of the Koopas.

00:31:21.819 --> 00:31:24.459
I demand that you release my father.

00:31:26.678 --> 00:31:29.208
Over my dead body.

00:31:29.208 --> 00:31:30.894
Fine with me.

00:31:44.630 --> 00:31:46.366
Why don't we start over?

00:31:46.366 --> 00:31:47.652
and introduce ourselves.

00:31:47.652 --> 00:31:50.397
Okay. um.
Hi. I'm Luigi.

00:31:51.141 --> 00:31:52.838
I'm Bowser Jr.

00:31:52.838 --> 00:31:54.980
And I'm gonna be taking my father

00:31:54.980 --> 00:31:55.505
now!

00:33:18.319 --> 00:33:22.575
You've doing so great.
but thought you might need a hand.

00:34:10.772 --> 00:34:11.897
Dad!

00:34:15.470 --> 00:34:16.795
Oh. God!

00:35:17.459 --> 00:35:18.824
Everyone okay?

00:35:22.237 --> 00:35:23.642
Where are we?

00:35:30.708 --> 00:35:33.040
Sweet! Freedom!

00:35:33.040 --> 00:35:34.862
You've gotta be kidding me.

00:35:34.862 --> 00:35:38.234
-Bye. suckers!
-Hey! Get back here!

00:35:38.234 --> 00:35:40.899
No! You can't catch the wind!

00:35:45.510 --> 00:35:47.020
I just kinda did.

00:35:47.020 --> 00:35:48.963
It was a metaphor!

00:35:58.542 --> 00:35:59.409
Stop it!

00:36:05.718 --> 00:36:07.351
You should probably spit him out

00:36:12.279 --> 00:36:13.283
whoo

00:36:14.593 --> 00:36:16.490
That was intense!

00:36:16.490 --> 00:36:19.512
Guys. this is embarrassing.

00:36:19.512 --> 00:36:22.318
I'm still a tiny work in progress.

00:36:22.318 --> 00:36:23.669
Sorry pal.

00:36:23.669 --> 00:36:25.743
Do you expect me to shake
the hand of the turtle...

00:36:25.743 --> 00:36:28.329
whose son just attacked me?

00:36:28.329 --> 00:36:29.713
My… son?

00:36:33.176 --> 00:36:35.183
I haven't seen him in years.

00:36:35.910 --> 00:36:39.093
Mario. I was a terrible father.

00:36:39.600 --> 00:36:41.005
He must hate me.

00:36:41.304 --> 00:36:42.290
Hate you?

00:36:42.410 --> 00:36:45.662
Your son tried to chop my head off
just to free you.

00:36:46.038 --> 00:36:47.348
He wants to see you.

00:36:47.902 --> 00:36:50.560
He could just use some guidance.

00:36:51.091 --> 00:36:52.499
Really?

00:36:52.499 --> 00:36:55.539
You think I might have
a shot at reconnecting with my boy?

00:36:56.337 --> 00:37:00.274
See. Mario? He's gotten really
in touch with his feelings.

00:37:00.274 --> 00:37:01.690
I'm drowning in them!

00:37:01.690 --> 00:37:03.532
Alright. Let's just keep moving.

00:37:03.533 --> 00:37:06.439
We gotta find a way off this planet
and get to Peach.

00:37:25.206 --> 00:37:27.013
Look! There it is!

00:37:38.230 --> 00:37:39.154
Oh!

00:37:49.802 --> 00:37:51.855
C'mon we're gonna be late

00:37:52.906 --> 00:37:53.789
Whoa.

00:37:54.118 --> 00:37:56.406
The Gateway Galaxy!

00:38:12.674 --> 00:38:14.714
Toad. where are you going?

00:38:14.715 --> 00:38:16.729
This must be who we're looking for.

00:38:19.913 --> 00:38:24.249
'Missing: Princess Rosalina'

00:38:35.488 --> 00:38:36.813
‘No! No!’

00:38:40.823 --> 00:38:43.674
Princess? Are you okay?

00:38:49.222 --> 00:38:51.390
Ukiki is lost.

00:38:51.926 --> 00:38:54.817
Have you seen Ukiki's friends?

00:38:55.453 --> 00:38:58.857
Aw! We've got a lost little monkey.

00:38:58.858 --> 00:39:00.890
I got ya. I got ya.

00:39:03.945 --> 00:39:06.903
That Monkey just used his cuteness
for crime

00:39:06.904 --> 00:39:10.330
-Toad! Wait!
-All our powerups and coins are in there!

00:39:10.688 --> 00:39:13.419
And my unfinished novel!

00:39:14.945 --> 00:39:17.033
-Pardon Me!
-Excuse me. Sorry.

00:39:19.062 --> 00:39:19.825
Gah!

00:39:27.518 --> 00:39:29.605
We got you now!

00:39:35.840 --> 00:39:37.144
Look. he jumped through the wall!

00:40:06.458 --> 00:40:07.823
Stay close.

00:40:29.901 --> 00:40:31.628
Hey! You!

00:40:32.973 --> 00:40:36.122
Hey! Give me my backpack!

00:40:47.725 --> 00:40:49.692
Dad. I know you're down there somewhere.

00:40:52.111 --> 00:40:54.625
Sire. it is hopeless.

00:40:54.626 --> 00:40:57.952
The important thing now in our
time of grief is to...

00:40:57.953 --> 00:41:01.439
stay strong for each other!

00:41:01.440 --> 00:41:05.909
Will you get a hold of yourself?
We gotta keep looking for Papa!

00:41:12.630 --> 00:41:15.802
So. um. Bowser wants to talk to you
about something.

00:41:18.352 --> 00:41:23.097
You know. Mario. all boys believe
their fathers are larger than life.

00:41:23.098 --> 00:41:26.715
I don't wanna disappoint my boy
by being so small.

00:41:26.716 --> 00:41:29.398
I'm not making you big.

00:41:29.399 --> 00:41:31.883
You're used to living a pine-sized life

00:41:32.417 --> 00:41:34.243
But I was born to be big!

00:41:34.718 --> 00:41:36.922
Undo the power of the Blue Mushroom

00:41:36.923 --> 00:41:40.408
and I shall fight by your side
for all of eternity.

00:41:40.409 --> 00:41:43.544
That's a good deal.
Eternity is a long time.

00:41:43.544 --> 00:41:45.862
We will be unstoppable!

00:41:45.863 --> 00:41:46.546
Mm.

00:41:47.115 --> 00:41:47.848
No

00:41:47.848 --> 00:41:50.241
Come on. hit me Mario.
Hit me.

00:41:50.242 --> 00:41:52.302
Now. Mario. Hit him.
We-we can trust him.

00:41:52.303 --> 00:41:54.870
-Hit me!
-Mario just go ahead. hit him. hit him.

00:41:55.463 --> 00:41:56.732
Hit me now!

00:41:56.733 --> 00:41:59.717
You tiny pathetic failure
of a plumber!

00:42:23.465 --> 00:42:25.593
You will not regret this.

00:42:30.500 --> 00:42:34.019
What're you guys waiting for?
There's a castle up there. Come on!

00:42:34.020 --> 00:42:35.039
Follow me!

00:42:48.608 --> 00:42:49.371
Sorry!

00:43:27.631 --> 00:43:28.594
Princess.

00:43:44.334 --> 00:43:45.418
Ukiki.

00:43:46.319 --> 00:43:48.608
Look at what you brought me.

00:43:52.703 --> 00:43:56.397
Princesses… are very valuable.

00:43:57.805 --> 00:44:00.319
Ukiki thinks your novel stinks.

00:44:00.320 --> 00:44:01.437
Ow! Ah!

00:44:06.822 --> 00:44:12.528
What is it with you "princesses"
and "getting captured"?

00:44:12.529 --> 00:44:14.884
You know something
about that missing princess?

00:44:15.398 --> 00:44:16.080
Mm.

00:44:17.238 --> 00:44:20.266
Not… a… thing.

00:44:21.245 --> 00:44:23.986
You listen to me. you slime ball!

00:44:23.987 --> 00:44:27.066
You're gonna tell me exactly
where Rosalina is.

00:44:27.067 --> 00:44:28.834
Or what?

00:45:01.017 --> 00:45:05.353
Oh. Princess.
You're going to regret that.

00:45:17.551 --> 00:45:18.274
Ha!

00:45:34.994 --> 00:45:36.439
Ha-ha!

00:46:22.602 --> 00:46:24.208
Ooh. yes!

00:46:50.774 --> 00:46:52.919
Where is she?

00:46:52.920 --> 00:46:54.990
Do I look like a snitch?

00:46:58.132 --> 00:47:01.312
-Oh! Yes. I do!
-This is your last chance.

00:47:01.313 --> 00:47:03.110
Okay. okay! Listen to me.

00:47:03.111 --> 00:47:05.483
-Bowser's kid took her.
-Where?

00:47:05.484 --> 00:47:07.412
The Space Junk Galaxy.

00:47:13.275 --> 00:47:15.563
-Toad.
-Give me that.

00:47:18.042 --> 00:47:21.125
Get me Bowser Jr. Now!

00:47:24.984 --> 00:47:26.951
Move those little legs. shortcake

00:47:30.487 --> 00:47:33.755
Hi. We need some help
getting off your planet.

00:47:33.756 --> 00:47:35.670
You will have to speak to the queen.

00:47:35.671 --> 00:47:38.303
But the scary looking guy stays here.

00:47:39.242 --> 00:47:40.755
I got this.

00:47:46.853 --> 00:47:48.959
Hello. Your Highness.

00:47:48.960 --> 00:47:51.847
We are trying to get to the Gateway Ga--

00:47:51.848 --> 00:47:56.083
You're the aliens.
who destroyed my flower fields.

00:47:56.084 --> 00:47:59.395
Imprison them!
Take them to the honey mines!

00:48:01.973 --> 00:48:04.173
Not on my watch!

00:48:07.229 --> 00:48:09.857
Someone must pay for their crimes.

00:48:09.858 --> 00:48:11.099
Release them!

00:48:11.100 --> 00:48:14.187
I shall serve their sentence
in their stead.

00:48:14.188 --> 00:48:18.680
I can do the work of a hundred men
and at least 10.000 bees.

00:48:18.681 --> 00:48:23.203
Take me. and send them
to the Gateway Galaxy.

00:48:29.737 --> 00:48:33.835
We have a deal.
Get them to the Gateway Galaxy!

00:48:36.837 --> 00:48:38.443
Are you sure about this?

00:48:41.113 --> 00:48:43.092
You're not as horrible
as I thought.

00:48:43.863 --> 00:48:44.813
Thank you.

00:48:46.145 --> 00:48:47.813
Put that away.

00:48:49.725 --> 00:48:51.571
You take care of him. okay?

00:48:52.007 --> 00:48:53.533
I always do.

00:48:53.534 --> 00:48:57.268
This miserable bug will give you passage.

00:49:04.186 --> 00:49:07.157
Go. Make your old enemy proud.

00:49:29.339 --> 00:49:32.350
When I'm free. me and my girl
are gonna go dancing

00:49:32.351 --> 00:49:33.765
till the sun rises.

00:49:34.055 --> 00:49:35.517
You got a honey back home?

00:49:37.217 --> 00:49:39.005
She bailed at the altar.

00:49:39.389 --> 00:49:41.316
Left me twisted in the wind.

00:49:41.317 --> 00:49:43.144
I'm still healing.

00:49:43.145 --> 00:49:45.358
Remembering who I was before her.

00:49:46.741 --> 00:49:48.369
That is one sensitive soul.

00:49:53.386 --> 00:49:54.189
Oh!

00:49:54.471 --> 00:49:57.723
Stay strong! You'll find
the right one someday.

00:50:06.435 --> 00:50:07.720
Hi. dad.

00:50:08.242 --> 00:50:09.394
Junior?

00:50:09.788 --> 00:50:11.876
Ho-ho-ho! My boy!

00:50:13.769 --> 00:50:15.535
You got so big.

00:50:16.606 --> 00:50:18.293
This is all yours?

00:50:20.246 --> 00:50:22.694
Hey. aren't you supposed to be
in boarding school?

00:50:22.695 --> 00:50:26.151
Boarding school? More like boring school.
I got expelled.

00:50:26.152 --> 00:50:27.191
Ha ha ha ha

00:50:27.686 --> 00:50:30.713
You really grew up
when I wasn't paying attention.

00:50:30.714 --> 00:50:36.268
Dad. we're about to become
the 2 most powerful dudes in the universe

00:50:36.269 --> 00:50:38.313
Remember when I was a baby turtle?

00:50:38.314 --> 00:50:41.466
You were working so hard trying
to conquer the world!

00:50:41.467 --> 00:50:43.653
But once in a while.
you'd have a night off.

00:50:43.654 --> 00:50:47.025
And you tucked me in and tell me
our favorite bedtime story.

00:50:47.547 --> 00:50:49.916
Those were the best nights of my life!

00:50:50.799 --> 00:50:52.280
Tell me the story.

00:50:52.281 --> 00:50:53.712
Again?

00:50:53.713 --> 00:50:54.359
ha ha ha.

00:51:08.188 --> 00:51:10.507
Back in the days of yore

00:51:10.508 --> 00:51:13.563
there was a powerful villain
with awesome hair.

00:51:14.051 --> 00:51:15.892
He loved conquering everything.

00:51:19.184 --> 00:51:21.713
You see. this villain had a son.

00:51:23.210 --> 00:51:27.373
The two roamed the universe
desperate for a place to call home.

00:51:27.374 --> 00:51:29.903
But everywhere they went
was just incredibly…

00:51:30.380 --> 00:51:31.349
Lame.

00:51:31.350 --> 00:51:32.473
Gross!

00:51:32.714 --> 00:51:35.588
So. they decided to make
their own planet!

00:51:35.589 --> 00:51:38.421
Behold! Planet Bowser!

00:51:38.422 --> 00:51:42.510
The sinister sanctuary where
they can spend the rest of the days.

00:51:42.867 --> 00:51:45.152
They built an evil roller coaster.

00:51:45.153 --> 00:51:47.204
A gorge full of lava.

00:51:47.205 --> 00:51:50.539
They carved a giant mountain
into the shape of their heads.

00:51:50.940 --> 00:51:55.410
And at the top of the planet.
they built the biggest cannon ever!

00:51:55.411 --> 00:51:58.208
It could destroy the universe!

00:51:59.198 --> 00:52:00.158
They called it…

00:52:00.159 --> 00:52:02.383
The Boomsday Weapon!

00:52:02.384 --> 00:52:04.393
To power it. they needed…

00:52:04.394 --> 00:52:07.562
The most powerful princess
in the universe!

00:52:08.176 --> 00:52:12.179
And when they had drained
all her power and the weapon was ready.

00:52:12.180 --> 00:52:14.182
They went planet by planet

00:52:14.183 --> 00:52:17.478
destroying all those
who disrespected them!

00:52:17.479 --> 00:52:18.374
Boom!

00:52:18.374 --> 00:52:19.269
Boom!

00:52:19.269 --> 00:52:20.164
Boom!

00:52:21.159 --> 00:52:26.219
Until they danced on the ashes of
the universe and reigned supreme!

00:52:26.813 --> 00:52:27.799
The end.

00:52:29.174 --> 00:52:31.735
Dad. will you tell me again tomorrow night.

00:52:31.736 --> 00:52:34.502
Of course. Good night. my boy.

00:52:38.918 --> 00:52:39.600
Shh.

00:52:41.337 --> 00:52:44.176
Dad. I built us that planet.

00:52:44.177 --> 00:52:45.301
You did?

00:52:45.301 --> 00:52:47.163
We're going there right now.

00:52:47.164 --> 00:52:49.797
You and me. Two Bowsers.

00:52:49.798 --> 00:52:51.067
No limits.

00:52:55.579 --> 00:52:57.386
My Lords.

00:52:57.845 --> 00:52:59.658
We have a problem.

00:53:16.852 --> 00:53:18.916
Welcome to the information booth.

00:53:18.917 --> 00:53:20.503
My name is Rob.

00:53:20.504 --> 00:53:22.709
Would you like some information?

00:53:22.709 --> 00:53:24.946
We need to find a pilot.
And quick.

00:53:24.947 --> 00:53:25.835
Certainly.

00:53:25.836 --> 00:53:28.103
Pilots can be found on the flight deck.

00:53:28.104 --> 00:53:33.714
Which is located right over…

00:53:38.084 --> 00:53:40.663
Oh. Rob. You're killing me.

00:53:40.664 --> 00:53:43.411
I'm sorry. I do not wish to kill you.

00:53:43.412 --> 00:53:44.847
Ugh. Toad!

00:53:44.848 --> 00:53:46.706
-I am Rob.
-I know!

00:53:46.707 --> 00:53:49.134
Great. Thanks for visiting
information.

00:53:49.135 --> 00:53:50.980
Where is the flight deck?

00:53:50.981 --> 00:53:53.440
Right over…

00:53:53.441 --> 00:53:54.541
Ugh!

00:53:55.934 --> 00:53:56.640
…here.

00:53:57.158 --> 00:53:59.246
-Thank you!
-You're welcome.

00:54:51.625 --> 00:54:55.084
Hi. there! Can you take us
to the Space Junk Galaxy?

00:54:55.085 --> 00:54:56.402
Uh. no.

00:54:58.301 --> 00:55:01.580
Excuse me. how much to take us
to the Space Junk Galaxy?

00:55:01.581 --> 00:55:03.633
Too dangerous for this little flyboy

00:55:04.347 --> 00:55:06.386
So. tell me this.

00:55:06.387 --> 00:55:10.490
Why is a princess trying to go to
the most dangerous place in the galaxy?

00:55:11.064 --> 00:55:12.524
Who are you?

00:55:12.524 --> 00:55:15.131
Don't ask me personal questions.

00:55:15.132 --> 00:55:16.244
Oh. I'm so sorry. I just--

00:55:16.245 --> 00:55:19.102
I'm Fox McCloud!

00:55:19.838 --> 00:55:23.889
Leader of the legendary Star Fox team!

00:55:23.890 --> 00:55:27.205
I only care about three things.
Keeping the Lylat system safe.

00:55:27.206 --> 00:55:32.891
fighting with my buds. and doing
extremely dangerous barrel rolls.

00:55:32.892 --> 00:55:34.056
Let's go!

00:55:34.420 --> 00:55:37.311
And one day. my warp drive exploded.

00:55:37.312 --> 00:55:39.762
blew a giant hole
in the fabric of space and time.

00:55:39.763 --> 00:55:42.054
and I got sucked into a different universe.

00:55:42.055 --> 00:55:44.223
That's what I get for making
a frog my engineer.

00:55:44.585 --> 00:55:48.129
And now I roam your galaxy.
trying to find a way home.

00:55:48.130 --> 00:55:51.081
Doing good. when the price is right.

00:55:52.034 --> 00:55:54.202
Oh. and I also have cool space boots.

00:55:54.671 --> 00:55:56.196
Whoa

00:55:56.586 --> 00:55:59.222
Now that's the backstory of
the guy who's going to take us

00:55:59.223 --> 00:56:00.885
to the Space Junk Galaxy.

00:56:01.277 --> 00:56:04.207
How desperate for money
do you think I am?

00:56:07.526 --> 00:56:08.869
Alright. you got a deal.

00:56:08.870 --> 00:56:10.136
I'll fuel up the Arwing.

00:56:10.137 --> 00:56:11.822
we'll take off in five.

00:56:15.757 --> 00:56:20.199
That was the coolest dude
I've ever seen.

00:56:26.217 --> 00:56:28.972
Mario. I have a great idea.

00:56:28.973 --> 00:56:30.203
When you see Peach.

00:56:30.204 --> 00:56:32.920
you should catch up and go.
"Bla-Bla-Bla..."

00:56:32.921 --> 00:56:34.274
"...oh. hi! How are you?"

00:56:34.275 --> 00:56:35.431
And then boom!

00:56:35.990 --> 00:56:38.680
You should ask her out on a date!

00:56:38.822 --> 00:56:43.117
I don't know. Lu. You think a princess
would have a date with a plumber?

00:56:44.276 --> 00:56:50.218
Mario. she would be the luckiest princess
in the world to be your girlfriend.

00:56:50.886 --> 00:56:52.670
She is going to say yes!

00:56:52.671 --> 00:56:56.348
And then you're going to ask her
if she has a friend for me!

00:56:57.906 --> 00:57:00.270
Now. we just need to find her.

00:57:00.970 --> 00:57:04.985
She is right over…

00:57:08.350 --> 00:57:09.635
Peach!

00:57:09.962 --> 00:57:11.395
Peach!

00:57:11.729 --> 00:57:13.931
Mario?

00:57:15.614 --> 00:57:18.459
Oh! Yoshi's here. Yay.

00:57:18.460 --> 00:57:19.993
Mario!

00:57:22.080 --> 00:57:23.285
A handshake?

00:57:23.847 --> 00:57:25.011
Thought it could be cool.

00:57:25.012 --> 00:57:28.964
I mean. just thought it could be cool.
th-that would be good.

00:57:29.311 --> 00:57:30.110
And cool.

00:57:30.111 --> 00:57:32.840
Mario. I found out where Rosalina is.

00:57:32.841 --> 00:57:34.928
And this guy is gonna take us there.

00:57:41.913 --> 00:57:43.335
Nice ride.

00:57:43.343 --> 00:57:44.644
Nice 'stache.

00:57:45.693 --> 00:57:47.058
Let's go.

00:57:51.602 --> 00:57:52.646
Wahoo!

00:58:07.554 --> 00:58:09.536
You gotta love a space rogue!

00:58:10.280 --> 00:58:11.933
He doesn't look like a rogue to me.

00:58:11.934 --> 00:58:14.359
He looks like Ms. Castellano's dog

00:58:14.366 --> 00:58:16.472
Can <i>Ms. Castellano's dog</i> do this?

00:58:21.707 --> 00:58:23.145
Wahoo!

00:58:23.719 --> 00:58:25.234
I like this guy!

00:58:40.990 --> 00:58:42.796
Might want to hang on to something.

00:59:21.497 --> 00:59:23.303
They're gonna pay for that!

00:59:28.414 --> 00:59:31.584
Wait. Junior! I kinda got to know them.

00:59:31.585 --> 00:59:33.243
They're super lame.

00:59:33.243 --> 00:59:35.308
but I still feel bad about killing them.

00:59:35.783 --> 00:59:38.263
What're you talking about.
not kill them?

00:59:39.303 --> 00:59:40.715
Well. that's weird.

00:59:40.716 --> 00:59:43.603
Okay. Doing this one for you Dad.

00:59:43.604 --> 00:59:47.289
When I'm done with them.
they'll be crying for their mommies.

00:59:47.290 --> 00:59:49.536
Uh. what's that gonna do?

00:59:57.255 --> 01:00:00.067
Bowser! He played us.

01:00:12.470 --> 01:00:14.317
Oh. babies!

01:00:24.482 --> 01:00:25.446
No!

01:00:25.447 --> 01:00:26.650
Boom!

01:00:32.511 --> 01:00:35.435
Don't worry. dad.
This time tomorrow.

01:00:35.436 --> 01:00:38.837
you'll have forgotten all about
those dorks in overalls.

01:00:38.838 --> 01:00:41.579
The whole universe will be ours!

01:01:06.656 --> 01:01:08.124
How 'bout now?

01:01:09.501 --> 01:01:10.464
Nope.

01:01:11.837 --> 01:01:13.684
Toad! The babies!

01:01:15.766 --> 01:01:16.769
On it!

01:01:22.465 --> 01:01:23.348
Come here!

01:01:38.102 --> 01:01:38.995
Huh?

01:01:52.954 --> 01:01:55.559
Yoshi! Come back!

01:01:55.560 --> 01:01:57.988
Yoshi. Yoshi. Yoshi!

01:02:09.074 --> 01:02:10.319
Come here.

01:02:14.469 --> 01:02:15.553
Luigi!

01:02:16.444 --> 01:02:17.810
What are you doing?

01:02:17.811 --> 01:02:18.850
Stop it!

01:02:27.747 --> 01:02:29.138
Mario!

01:02:57.088 --> 01:02:59.698
Yoshi!

01:03:30.358 --> 01:03:32.029
L-Let go! Let go! Let go!

01:03:32.029 --> 01:03:34.864
Give it! Give it!
Give it to me! Give it to--

01:04:52.441 --> 01:04:53.847
Oh. uh.

01:04:57.627 --> 01:04:59.626
I kinda liked being a baby.

01:04:59.627 --> 01:05:03.529
All the scary thoughts running through
my head just disappeared. you know.

01:05:05.116 --> 01:05:07.665
We're gonna fix you up like new. okay?

01:05:07.666 --> 01:05:09.985
It's gonna be fine.
It's just a dent.

01:05:09.986 --> 01:05:12.234
Just a dent

01:05:21.759 --> 01:05:25.172
Hey. we are gonna find a way
off this planet.

01:05:25.173 --> 01:05:27.944
Mario. we're galaxies away
from Rosalina.

01:05:27.945 --> 01:05:29.654
We can't fix the ship.

01:05:29.655 --> 01:05:32.586
And somehow. we keep
adding dinosaurs!

01:05:34.092 --> 01:05:35.488
I know you're frustrated.

01:05:35.489 --> 01:05:37.259
Princesses don't get frustrated!

01:05:38.307 --> 01:05:41.519
 Alright. but then can I be
not frustrated with you?

01:05:50.096 --> 01:05:52.926
Uh. Breaker. Breaker. this is
Big Green with Little Red

01:05:52.927 --> 01:05:53.893
and the League of Beagle.

01:05:53.894 --> 01:05:57.254
We are looking for an EVAC ASAP.

01:05:57.255 --> 01:05:59.731
Had a major fender bender in
Dino Town.

01:05:59.732 --> 01:06:01.419
Uh. we're hauling some low cargo--

01:06:03.216 --> 01:06:05.705
Come on! You can do it!

01:06:12.192 --> 01:06:13.305
Woohoo

01:06:16.157 --> 01:06:19.369
Look what happens when you don't
have a bedtime!

01:06:20.949 --> 01:06:21.897
'Mayday. Mayday.'

01:06:21.898 --> 01:06:24.788
This is the big Luigi-dog saying
“over and out”

01:06:24.789 --> 01:06:26.678
Luigi?

01:06:36.240 --> 01:06:38.352
Their mustaches were ridiculous.

01:06:38.353 --> 01:06:40.441
But they weren't bad guys.

01:06:41.135 --> 01:06:42.416
They were your friends. huh?

01:06:43.476 --> 01:06:46.045
Nothing's more dangerous
than a friend.

01:06:46.046 --> 01:06:49.539
When your armor's down.
they'll stab you in the back.

01:06:49.953 --> 01:06:51.639
Where did you hear that?

01:06:51.640 --> 01:06:55.226
It's what you told me when you dropped me
off for my first day at school.

01:06:55.579 --> 01:06:57.279
I am a good dad.

01:06:57.860 --> 01:07:01.306
Those friends of yours tried to ruin you.

01:07:01.307 --> 01:07:03.216
Turned you into something you're not.

01:07:03.651 --> 01:07:05.919
You know who won't hurt you?

01:07:05.920 --> 01:07:07.316
Your family.

01:07:07.740 --> 01:07:10.158
Family is forever.

01:07:10.673 --> 01:07:11.998
Close your eyes.

01:07:17.887 --> 01:07:18.690
Dad!

01:07:19.408 --> 01:07:20.528
Wait for it.

01:07:21.701 --> 01:07:23.147
Now open.

01:07:41.203 --> 01:07:42.203
Guys.

01:07:42.567 --> 01:07:45.799
There's something extremely weird
flying towards us.

01:08:06.515 --> 01:08:08.001
Let's-a go!

01:08:26.266 --> 01:08:29.999
We'll be at Space Junk Galaxy
before naptime.

01:09:12.387 --> 01:09:16.613
'Once upon a time. there was
a brave and noble princess'

01:09:16.614 --> 01:09:18.752
'named Peach.’

01:09:21.694 --> 01:09:25.124
'Her story begins many years ago'

01:09:26.190 --> 01:09:29.712
'when she lived on a small planet
with her sister. Rosalina.'

01:09:31.459 --> 01:09:34.608
'The two sisters were made
of stardust.'

01:09:39.616 --> 01:09:44.012
‘Their love burned as brightly
as the stars themselves.’

01:09:46.007 --> 01:09:50.308
'Together. they could summon
the power of the cosmos.'

01:10:03.399 --> 01:10:06.871
'But evil forces wanted
the power for themselves.'

01:10:09.518 --> 01:10:13.607
‘Rosalina… had to send Peach away'

01:10:13.608 --> 01:10:15.134
'to safety.

01:10:24.597 --> 01:10:27.929
'No! No! No!’

01:10:32.140 --> 01:10:34.926
'The Toads raised and protected her'

01:10:34.927 --> 01:10:38.681
'until she grew strong enough
to protect them.'

01:10:56.229 --> 01:11:00.623
Dad. welcome to Planet Bowser!

01:11:19.935 --> 01:11:22.082
You really built all this?

01:11:22.083 --> 01:11:23.180
But that's not all.

01:11:23.181 --> 01:11:27.815
We have our very own
Boomsday Weapon!

01:11:30.690 --> 01:11:34.606
And the princess I kidnapped
to power it!

01:11:38.625 --> 01:11:41.579
The universe will never forgive you!

01:11:41.580 --> 01:11:45.172
This is who you are.
This is where you belong.

01:11:45.645 --> 01:11:48.671
Tonight. we destroy
the Mushroom Kingdom.

01:11:48.672 --> 01:11:50.750
tomorrow. the universe!

01:12:01.149 --> 01:12:04.281
Yeah! Long live the King!

01:12:05.386 --> 01:12:07.112
They're waiting for you.

01:12:09.521 --> 01:12:14.580
Sometimes. on this rainbow road
of life. we lose our way.

01:12:14.581 --> 01:12:16.416
But if you're lucky.

01:12:16.417 --> 01:12:20.620
a tiny version of yourself
helps you remember your true calling.

01:12:22.180 --> 01:12:27.051
My Koopas! Your king has returned!

01:13:33.983 --> 01:13:35.870
We'll get you on the planet.

01:13:36.259 --> 01:13:39.752
Buckle up. It's about to get crazy.

01:13:41.584 --> 01:13:44.354
Star Fox team is ready!

01:13:46.411 --> 01:13:47.839
Sick.

01:13:48.959 --> 01:13:49.682
Come on!

01:14:14.724 --> 01:14:16.400
Let's do this.

01:14:21.885 --> 01:14:23.972
Incoming!

01:14:27.107 --> 01:14:29.155
Do a barrel roll!

01:14:31.982 --> 01:14:33.186
Yay!

01:14:43.576 --> 01:14:45.149
You're up. Mustache!

01:14:45.150 --> 01:14:46.026
Good luck!

01:15:10.243 --> 01:15:11.568
Wahoo!

01:15:30.984 --> 01:15:33.760
I don't know what that means.

01:15:33.761 --> 01:15:36.282
It means you go this way.
we go that way.

01:15:36.283 --> 01:15:37.528
Oh. got ya.

01:16:28.379 --> 01:16:31.189
Intruder alert! Intruder alert!

01:16:36.617 --> 01:16:38.504
It won't be long now. Dad.

01:16:38.505 --> 01:16:39.270
Ahem.

01:16:39.270 --> 01:16:40.456
What?

01:16:40.457 --> 01:16:43.968
My Lords. our tormentors
have returned!

01:16:45.652 --> 01:16:47.338
I'll take care of 'em.

01:16:48.077 --> 01:16:51.329
I built a security system
that's next level.

01:16:54.881 --> 01:16:57.250
They're gonna get torn to pieces!

01:16:58.665 --> 01:17:00.472
I love being a dad.

01:17:00.473 --> 01:17:04.394
Oh. the days are long.
but the years are short.

01:17:25.673 --> 01:17:28.323
'Hello. Peach and Mario.'

01:17:30.342 --> 01:17:33.391
Prepare to meet your maker.

01:18:44.706 --> 01:18:46.267
I've got you now.

01:19:23.458 --> 01:19:26.228
I won't let them ruin this.

01:19:47.991 --> 01:19:51.348
Bowser!

01:19:51.349 --> 01:19:53.171
Didn't have to be this way.

01:19:53.172 --> 01:19:56.404
I know there's still
some good in there.

01:20:02.970 --> 01:20:04.987
Let us pass. Now!

01:20:04.988 --> 01:20:08.818
Or what? You'll humiliate me
at my wedding?

01:20:08.819 --> 01:20:11.642
You shrink me to a nubbin
and put me in a jar?

01:20:11.643 --> 01:20:14.156
Make me join a book club?

01:20:14.157 --> 01:20:16.199
We had our moment. Mario.

01:20:16.200 --> 01:20:18.087
But Bowser is back.

01:20:18.088 --> 01:20:21.237
And now you'll feel my fury!

01:20:41.995 --> 01:20:44.982
No. No. No!

01:20:47.631 --> 01:20:48.755
Dad!

01:21:08.745 --> 01:21:09.910
Dad.

01:21:31.226 --> 01:21:33.823
I am the Lord of Bones!

01:21:33.824 --> 01:21:36.171
I am the Skull King!

01:21:36.172 --> 01:21:38.746
And I am his son!

01:21:54.062 --> 01:21:55.225
Mario!

01:21:57.120 --> 01:21:59.650
Go. Save her.

01:23:10.915 --> 01:23:11.956
Ow!

01:23:14.184 --> 01:23:15.577
Yoshi.

01:23:20.623 --> 01:23:21.868
Very weird.

01:24:23.169 --> 01:24:24.052
Ow!

01:24:28.344 --> 01:24:29.910
Finish this. Lu.

01:24:36.185 --> 01:24:36.829
Lu!?

01:24:36.830 --> 01:24:40.564
What? You know
I never learned how to draw.

01:24:51.514 --> 01:24:52.317
Yes!

01:24:53.283 --> 01:24:54.528
No!

01:25:29.383 --> 01:25:31.752
In the name of the Koopas--

01:25:34.975 --> 01:25:35.889
Junior?

01:25:35.890 --> 01:25:39.433
Daddy! Please help me!

01:25:43.494 --> 01:25:45.582
Junior!

01:26:13.077 --> 01:26:14.602
Ha-ha-ha!

01:26:18.577 --> 01:26:19.840
Dad!

01:26:19.841 --> 01:26:21.567
Oh. my boy!

01:26:52.724 --> 01:26:54.290
Rosalina!

01:27:01.433 --> 01:27:04.002
I need you to try!

01:27:56.201 --> 01:27:58.690
I knew you would come for me.

01:28:01.978 --> 01:28:04.744
Hey! Found your femur. Dad!

01:28:04.745 --> 01:28:06.079
Doing great. my boy!

01:28:06.080 --> 01:28:07.525
Let's find my foot.

01:28:08.861 --> 01:28:10.027
Mario!

01:28:10.028 --> 01:28:12.839
Mario! Come meet my sister.

01:28:13.545 --> 01:28:15.899
I'm so happy you found each other.

01:28:15.900 --> 01:28:18.309
I love a family reunion!

01:28:18.665 --> 01:28:20.258
-Hey-o!
-Hey-o!

01:28:31.842 --> 01:28:33.488
Mama?

01:28:36.996 --> 01:28:38.562
My babies!

01:28:39.293 --> 01:28:41.050
We missed you so much!

01:28:41.051 --> 01:28:42.760
I missed you too.

01:28:42.761 --> 01:28:45.969
Mama. can we visit the Mushroom Kingdom?

01:28:45.970 --> 01:28:48.194
I wanna see the castle.

01:28:48.195 --> 01:28:50.002
Okay. okay.

01:28:56.753 --> 01:28:58.720
Where's your castle?

01:29:00.298 --> 01:29:03.537
Ah. well the castle. Yeah. the castle
Um...

01:29:03.538 --> 01:29:04.863
it died!

01:29:06.770 --> 01:29:09.238
What're you talking about?

01:29:09.238 --> 01:29:11.606
You know what guys?
We're gonna rebuild

01:29:11.607 --> 01:29:14.703
the best castle ever!
Who wants to help?

01:29:19.666 --> 01:29:21.633
-Oh. yeah!
-Whoo-hoo!

01:29:58.406 --> 01:29:59.932
Wahoo!

01:32:25.159 --> 01:32:27.159
So. where are you off to next?

01:32:27.160 --> 01:32:30.610
That nice Space Princess fixed up my warp drive
and I'm heading home

01:32:32.617 --> 01:32:34.007
Good luck with them.

01:32:34.008 --> 01:32:36.796
That is one complicated family.

01:32:45.418 --> 01:32:47.018
Don't worry son.

01:32:47.019 --> 01:32:49.208
No jail can hold us.

01:32:49.209 --> 01:32:51.209
We'll be out of here soon.

01:32:59.320 --> 01:33:00.956
Hello. Maggots.

01:33:00.957 --> 01:33:02.567
Trying to escape?

01:33:03.456 --> 01:33:05.996
You're gonna play by my rules now.

01:33:05.997 --> 01:33:08.575
Stay close son.
she won't break us

01:33:08.587 --> 01:33:11.500
First goes the body then goes the bones

01:33:12.302 --> 01:33:14.934
Then all that's left is dust.

01:33:14.935 --> 01:33:17.268
You be quiet. right now!

01:33:17.269 --> 01:33:19.650
You can't silence the truth.

01:33:19.651 --> 01:33:21.541
It only makes it louder.

01:33:21.542 --> 01:33:23.841
Like the approaching drumbeat

01:33:23.842 --> 01:33:25.656
of Death!

01:33:26.411 --> 01:33:29.422
Boom. boom. boom. boom.

01:37:39.645 --> 01:37:41.345
Now. there there.

01:37:41.346 --> 01:37:43.022
You poor little monkey.

01:37:47.268 --> 01:37:48.434
Ha ha ha ha--

01:37:52.613 --> 01:37:55.362
Well thank you very much

01:37:55.363 --> 01:37:56.696
Your Highness.
